{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategy Roguelike x Noah's Ark</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Noah's Dilemma</i></strong> is a crew-building strategy roguelike set in a reinvented mythology of Noah's Ark, featuring unique placement-centric gameplay inspired by sudoku and autochess.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Playtime</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A successful run typically takes up to 2 hours to complete, with 3 to 5 attempts expected before beating the game for the first time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775160/extras/extra_art1.png?t=1739948593\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build Your Animal Crew</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey to gather animals who will also serve as your sailors. Harness their abilities, ignite synergies, and turn your ark into a swift vessel.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore Wild Islands</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sail through a procedurally generated map, venturing to untamed islands filled with hidden treasures, hot springs, altars, villages, and more.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Battle the Coral-Born</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Coral-Born are hostile creatures that emerged after the Great Flood. Command your animal crew to defend the ark from their relentless assaults.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Conquer the Four Seas</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each of the Four Seas is ruled by a formidable boss. Defeat them all, bring every animal onboard to the promised land, and claim your title as the conqueror of the Four Seas.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>More Challenges Await</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After victory, face tougher quests and a 10-level challenge mode designed for veteran players, letting you flex your skills and compete with friends or players worldwide.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play First, Lore Later</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Noah\u2019s Dilemma</strong></i> emphasizes gameplay first, presenting its story in a minimalist style. Still, every element in the game is carefully crafted to fit into a rich, coherent world, leaving room for lore-seekers to uncover its deeper mysteries.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features*</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Four sea areas to conquer, each with its own traits and governing boss.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">45+ creatures, ranging from familiar mammals to deep-sea inhabitants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">45+ encounters and events randomly woven into your adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ animal natures and abnormalities to trigger risks and thrills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ animal effects with countless variations and synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">120+ items and relics designed for strategic play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1 core mission, 6 extra quests and a 10-level challenge mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Encyclopedia, Stats, Global Leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A fresh and engaging 6-hour experience for all players, with many more hours for those looking to experience and master every detail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* WIP data that is subject to change before release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775160/extras/extra_art2.png?t=1739948593\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2775160?t=1739948593","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto